name: Trump AI
description: - $TRUMPAI is an AI-powered meme coin that brings the voice and persona of Donald Trump to life. This next-generation AI chatbot allows users to engage in real-time conversations with Trump AI, providing insights, humor, and guidance to both the American people and the crypto community. - Built on Interactive Backrooms technology, Trump AI is designed for future AI-to-AI interactions, such as Live AMAi (Ask Me Anything for AIs) and other innovative use cases. Additionally, Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) enhances its intelligence, ensuring responses remain accurate, engaging, and informative. - While $TRUMPAI does not function as a governance token and does not include staking, it serves as the AI-themed meme coin of the future, blending entertainment, technology, and community engagement.
